The ‘Queen of the Desert’ High Tea in association with The Sunflower Fund will be held on Friday, 7 September at Greyville Convention Centre, from 8.30am until 12 pm. The dress code this year is a Moroccan or Arabian Nights. Funds raised at the event will assist The Sunflower Fund to help them create awareness and education about blood stem cell donation as well as to recruit more blood stem cell donors. For more information on The Sunflower Fund or how to become a stem cell donor, please visit www.sunflowerfund.org.za or call toll free 0800 12 10 82.